stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    [*] --> created: Issue accepted

    created --> running: Devin session\ncreated

    state running {
        direction TB
        working --> pr_ready: PR detected
        working --> waiting_for_user: Devin asks question
        working --> waiting_for_approval: Needs approval
        pr_ready --> waiting_for_user: Devin asks question
        pr_ready --> working: Still iterating
        waiting_for_user --> working: User responds
        waiting_for_approval --> working: Approved
    }

    running --> completed: exit / finished
    running --> failed: error / suspended
    running --> timed_out: Timeout exceeded

    completed --> [*]
    failed --> [*]
    timed_out --> [*]
